      "actionDate": "2025-12-02",
      "actionDesc": "Public Law",
      "text": "<p>This joint resolution requests the Department of the Interior to authorize the display of U.S. semiquincentennial materials and other significant artifacts, digital content, film footage, and associated audio and imagery in and around the vicinity of the National Mall during the period beginning on December 31, 2025, and ending on January 5, 2026.</p>",
